snippet.title: Cave Digger: Riches teaser - Chaos Gauntlet
snippet.description:
The frontiers of Cave Digger: Riches are opening for the brave miners on 30th of August! Discover new tools, upgrades, secrets, treasures and multiple endings (if you're able to figure out them all). 

Cave Digger: Riches on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/870600/Cave_Digger_Riches_DLC/

CD:R Supporter's edition:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/894780/Cave_Digger_Riches_Supporters_Edition/

Play Cave Digger for free: https://store.steampowered.com/app/844380/Cave_Digger/

Follow us on
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/cavediggergame/
Twitter https://twitter.com/vr_kiwi
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/cavedigger_vr/
